  "_comment": "Hand-edit. Maps a ticker to the company NAMES Trump (or anyone) might use in prose. Without this, ticker extraction only catches $CASHTAGS and ALL-CAPS symbols — but people write 'Intel' / 'Apple' / 'Nvidia', not 'INTC' / 'AAPL' / 'NVDA'. Names are matched case-insensitively on word boundaries. Keep names specific to avoid false positives (e.g. don't add 'gap' or 'target'). DJT is deliberately excluded — Trump signs every post 'President DJT'.",
